reviewText: Kinda an old drama, but I enjoyed it. Nice eye candy!
Very cute drama to watch. Love the clothes that the characters wear in this drama! Glad to be owning this korean drama!
Exactly what I wanted. With english subtitles. Great! If you don't like reading subtitles, I don't recommend it. The music is highly addictive.
This TV drama is really nice has a nice story a lot of people could relate to it. Great cast, full of fun for all the family.
